&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;CoreWeave’s Engaged Accounts team manages and grows a book of active, billing customers across infrastructure and software. The team is built to deepen existing customer relationships, protect revenue, and expand consumption through a portfolio model supported by technical and cross-functional specialists.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Account Manager owns a portfolio of 15–30 active customer accounts spanning CoreWeave infrastructure and Weights &amp;amp; Biases software. This role is responsible for the day-to-day health, retention, renewal, and expansion of those accounts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a customer-facing role for someone who can manage a book of business while driving commercial execution across infrastructure and software motions. The right candidate will build durable, multi-threaded relationships, manage renewals and expansions, and coordinate internal resources to keep customers successful and growing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you will:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own and grow a portfolio of 15–30 billing customers across CoreWeave infrastructure and Weights &amp;amp; Biases software.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive expansion, and retention across your book, protecting and growing recurring revenue.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify, shape, negotiate, and close expansion opportunities within existing accounts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain multi-threaded relationships across technical and business stakeholders within each customer.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor account health, usage, and consumption trends, and drive adoption to reduce churn risk.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Orchestrate CoreWeave resources — Solutions Architects, Technical Solutions Managers, support, and product specialists — to resolve issues and unlock growth across your portfolio.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead commercial conversations and negotiations for renewals and expansions across infrastructure and software.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Forecast and report on portfolio revenue, renewals, and expansion pipeline against your targets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner cross-functionally with Technical, Business Development, Professional Services, and Partners to deliver customer outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
