&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;6+ years of sales, account management, or customer-facing commercial experience in cloud, infrastructure, SaaS, AI platform, or related technology markets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience managing a book or portfolio of multiple active customer accounts simultaneously.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated track record of driving retention, renewals, and expansion revenue.&lt;/li&gt;
