&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Manager, Self Perform, you will manage the delivery of construction projects across CoreWeave’s growing portfolio of data center campuses. You will lead projects from initial site feasibility and pre-development planning through design, permitting, construction, and final closeout. This role sits at the intersection of strategic planning and hands-on execution—you will be accountable for managing project budgets, coordinating stakeholder relationships, and ensuring projects align with CoreWeave’s aggressive infrastructure roadmap.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In this role, you will:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
