&lt;li&gt;Manage and track project budgets and assist in securing expenditure approvals across all project phases.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support General Contractor and subcontractor bid processes, including market research and contract negotiation support to ensure competitive and high-quality partnerships.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate external consultants and specialty vendors, including architects, structural and MEP engineers, and legal counsel.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support pre-construction activities, including design reviews and regulatory permitting in partnership with local jurisdictions and authorities.&lt;/li&gt;
