&lt;li&gt;Assemble, rack, cable, and install enterprise-grade servers, networking equipment, and supporting infrastructure.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform hardware upgrades, preventative maintenance, and equipment replacements to maximize system reliability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Learn to automate operational tasks by developing or modifying scripts that support server and network operations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Investigate hardware and software failures, perform root cause analysis, and help implement long-term solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow industry-leading safety, security, and operational best practices while working in a mission-critical data center.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This apprenticeship is more than an introduction to IT - it’s an opportunity to build a strong technical foundation, develop sought-after data center and infrastructure skills, and launch a career supporting the cutting-edge technology that powers the future of AI.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
