&lt;p&gt;We’re constantly opening new data centers and expanding our teams, so flexibility or uncertainty around location is completely okay.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re always excited to connect with people who are passionate about data center operations, hardware, and infrastructure. This interest form is for individuals who would like to be considered for future or upcoming Data Center Technician opportunities at CoreWeave.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you enjoy hands-on technical work, problem-solving, and being part of a fast-growing environment, we’d love to learn more about you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
