&lt;li&gt;Participating in an on-call rotation and providing after-hours support as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Occasional travel to other data center locations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a salaried, &lt;strong&gt;fully onsite&lt;/strong&gt; role at one of our data center locations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
